#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:170
msgid ""
"There's a growing trend of customers paying bills later and later. "
"Therefore, collectors must make every effort to collect money and collect it"
" faster."
msgstr ""
"Les clients ont tendance à payer leurs factures de plus en plus tard. Par "
"conséquent, les agents de recouvrement doivent faire tout leur possible pour"
